Acts ch. 80, sec. 1, effective July 15, 1982; ch. 237, sec. 1, effective July 15, 1982; ch. 413, sec. 1, effective July 15, 1982; and ch. 419, sec. 4, effective July 15, 1982. -- Amended 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 161, sec. 3, effective July 15, 1980. -- Amended 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 384, sec. 75, effective June 17, 1978. -- Amended 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 74, Art. VI, sec. 107(1). -- Created 1972 Ky. metadata.lrc-note: (7/14/92). This section was amended by the 1992 Regular Session of the General Assembly and also repealed. Pursuant to KRS 446.260, the repeal prevails.
